data.description: Your still looking for it, aren't you? You know, for that property with a couple of acres, situated in a peaceful and private country setting, complete with ample space for gardening, raising a few chickens, or simply enjoying the outdoors. The one featuring a single-level brick home, 3 BR and 1.5 BA, family room w/ built in gas fireplace, wide galley kitchen, a sun-drenched sunroom that leads to your backyard oasis - where you will enjoy sipping your morning coffee on the expansive patio or maybe take a dip in the in-ground salt water pool (5 1/2 ft deep). 2 separate wired workshops/storage buildings (16X20 & 8X10), and a separate dedicated electric RV hookup w/ water source.... Stop looking. It's.Right.Here. Located just outside the town limits of picturesque Hickory Grove SC, you will find it's an easy ride to York, Rock Hill, Gaffney & I-85. Assumable 2.875% VA loan! Ask for details!
